          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1635764948230-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1635764948230-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p><p>Top, tail, peel, then grate your<strong> carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Add the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>grated carrot</strong> and<strong> sliced spring onion</strong> to a large mixing bowl</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1009.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1009.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1009.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
