            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once browned, reduce the heat to medium-low and sprinkle your<strong> five-spice</strong> <strong>mix</strong> over the chicken and turn several times until evenly coated in the spice</p><p>Cook for 1 min further, then add a splash of <strong>water</strong> and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1635764952740-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1635764952740-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1635764952740-x700.jpg",
