          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1635764952740-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> into discs</p><p>Stack a few <strong>cucumber discs</strong> at a time and cut each stack into <strong>matchsticks</strong></p><p>Cut <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli[es]</strong> into rounds (save the rest for later!)</p><p>Add the<strong> cucumber matchsticks</strong> and <strong>chilli rounds</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the bowl with the shredded lettuce,<strong> </strong>carrot and spring onion – this is your <strong>crunchy salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1009.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1009.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1009.-step-5-x700.jpg",
